-- Geithner says vital to sustain recovery efforts
-- 
-- Tue Jul 14, 2009 5:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/14/us-gulf-usa-geithner-recovery-sb-idUSTRE56D1L620090714

 

 JEDDAH  (Reuters) - U.S. Treasury Secretary Timothy Geithner said on Tuesday there was a need to sustain efforts to promote the global economy's recovery. 

 He also said he was seeing a return of confidence to the U.S. banking systems, and an increase in corporate bond issuance.